Class DiceNumber

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Number
diceTools.DiceNumber
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<java.lang.Number>
Direct Known Subclasses:
DiceNumber.DiceDouble, DiceNumber.DiceInteger
public abstract class DiceNumber
extends java.lang.Number
implements java.lang.Comparable<java.lang.Number>
Number which can store either an int or double, and which is aware of the data representation of the number it stores.
